Tammy MacIntosh https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tammy_MacIntosh 0 Tammy MacIntosh (born 16 February 1970) is an Australian actress who is perhaps best known for portraying Dr. Charlotte Beaumont in the medical drama All Saints and Jool in the TV series Farscape. She is also known for her roles on television series The Flying Doctors, Police Rescue, Sea Patrol, the television film McLeod's Daughters which led to the acclaimed drama series of the same title, and is currently appearing in role of Kaz Proctor in the prison drama series Wentworth.
